{"tid":977761,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"潮州廢老：樓市波動厲害 籲千萬不要炒樓","createTime":"2019-01-11T12:08:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T14:39:17.000Z","uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e8713e27472586908a7100102b282dd1989880a","tid":977761,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:08:05.000Z","msg":"長實前主席李嘉誠預料，今年世界經濟環境複雜及差，可能有很多國家都要面對低增長，呼籲市民要小心。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉誠又指，自己對香港樓市維持一貫的看法，贊成負擔得到分期付款、有能力的市民置業，但需量力而為；至於炒賣樓宇就千萬不可，因樓市波動會較厲害。他又指享受退休生活，亦感十分高興。"},{"pid":"8fe5f4dcc5419864724abfd8dd3c82b24de36f65","tid":977761,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:12:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1e6cde60a9e6a6d7f90be908063b74c1d820898","tid":977761,"uid":76855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"Nice title"},{"pid":"00b12109463eeb2c5fdfa394c01c1787ffd6a80c","tid":977761,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T12:20:58.000Z","msg":"林太比呢d廢老更有智慧<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUhAtBA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUhAtBA.png&h=7c610507&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VQAZaPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVQAZaPW.png&h=01b578c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64eb9704673e17d0f2929f1e95373c698d464737","tid":977761,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:06:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b0111c5847badb0411366f4f0aeb39c763fe177","tid":977761,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:39:17.000Z","msg":"潮洲黑心廢淡， bu 喇麼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}